                "Content": "<color=#37FFFF>Paimon: </color>Whew, Port Ormos definitely has a different vibe to Sumeru City...<br><color=#37FFFF>Paimon: </color>It's a bustling area, and there's so many outlanders. Plus, no one needs to spend all their time buried in their studies, which is nice.<br><color=#37FFFF>Traveler: </color>Yes, but that's why they end up being disciplined by the port authorities. So you see, Paimon? If you don't study hard, you'll end up just like them!<br><color=#37FFFF>Paimon: </color>Oh...<br><color=#37FFFF>Paimon: </color>Wait! What was that tone of voice for!?",
