                "Content": "<color=#37FFFF>Baizhu:</color> What lovely weather. Which reminds me, we just received a batch of herbs...<br><color=#37FFFF>Changsheng:</color> Don't worry, even if Qiqi forgot to dry out the herbs, Herbalist Gui will certainly remember to put them out in the sun.<br><color=#37FFFF>Baizhu:</color> Hehe. Yes, you're right.",
